[I] A runtime code generator for RISC-V

[T] This allows for runtime code generation of RISC-V instructions. 
[T] Similar to how Xbyak allows for runtime code generation of x86 instructions.

[U] https://github.com/lioncash/biscuit

[A] lioncash {https://github.com/lioncash}
[M] andrei32

[C] extra/development
[F] CROSS
[R] + riscv riscv64

[L] MIT
[V] 0.19.0 0ac545d
[P] X -----5---9 200.000

[D] 9a4b5b43e6c2118e217781a52905b028fcd700742277fa39392a23cf biscuit-0.19.0-0ac545d.tar.gz https://github.com/lioncash/biscuit/archive/0ac545d/

var_append cmakeopt ' ' "-DBISCUIT_CODE_BUFFER_MMAP=ON -DBUILD_SHARED_LIBS=ON"
var_append cmakeopt ' ' "-DBUILD_TESTING=FALSE -DBUILD_DEXAMPLES=FALSE"

hook_add prepatch 5 "cp -v $confdir/biscuit.pc.in src/"
